# PHProjectTextElement

**Class**

An element that represents text within project section content.

## Declaration

```swift
class PHProjectTextElement
```

## Describing a Text Element

- **text**: The raw unformatted string for the text element.
- **attributedText**: The stylized attributed string for the text element as presented to the user in Photos.
- **textElementType**: The enumerated type of the text element.
- **PHProjectTextElement.ElementType**: An enumeration of the type of text element.

## Subclassing Project Elements

- **PHProjectAssetElement**: An element that represents a media asset within project section content.
- **PHProjectJournalEntryElement**: An element that represents a journal entry within project section content.
- **PHProjectMapElement**: An element that represents a map within project section content.
